Visualisation:
X axis is length of number_of_comments
Y axis is positive_comments_percents + negative_comments_percents

Visualisation libs:
import numpy as np # Import numpy lib
from numpy import convolve # 
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

plt.style.use('ggplot')

x = [1, 2, 3]
y = [1, 2, 3]

# Draw 
plt.plot(x, y, 'o-')
plt.show()

